- "Total weight of their harvest" refers to the cumulative number of reports they have generated.

- 'blossomed in the digital garden after 1990' refers to programming languages released after 1990;
- 'outshone the expected glow' refers to having an average popularity score higher than the predicted popularity;
- 'threshold of attention for a 'popularity' alert' refers to the threshold value set for triggering a popularity alert;
